  <source>National Health Research Institutes, Taiwan</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      1. To establish a pathology reference laboratory for the consultation on the diagnosis of
           infectious diseases and lymphoma.

        2. To study the specific pathogens on 100 cases of unexplained death due to infectious
           diseases in the files of Taiwan CDC and the Forensic Institutes of Department of Law and
           Justice.

        3. To study the distribution of children lymphoid lesions in Vietnam and Taiwan and their
           virus association.

        4. To establish a tissue bank for infectious diseases and lymphoma.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
